title: #154 - Halloween Extravaganza & Candy Tier List
description:
On this episode of The H3 Podcast the gang go all out for Halloween and each dress up as some of their favorite memes from the H3 canon. We also give the DEFINITIVE Halloween candy tier list, check in with SoFlo Antonio, watch some Turkish food videos, settle the anal fissure debate, and a whole lot more!
